             class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline flex items-center gap-1">
            ğŸ“Š P: HuggingFace Stats
          </a>
          <a href="/methodology#velocity" 
             class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline flex items-center gap-1">
            ğŸ“ˆ V: 7-Day Delta
          </a>
          <a href="https://paperswithcode.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
             class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline flex items-center gap-1">
            ğŸ“„ C: Papers With Code
          </a>
          <a href="/methodology#utility"
             class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline flex items-center gap-1">
            ğŸ”§ U: Deploy Score
